  Short Bio  
Xiaohui Xie is a full profesor in the Department of Computer Science at UC Irvine, where he has
been since 2007. He received his PhD from MIT, and completed his postdoctoral
training at the Broad Institute of MIT and Harvard. He is interested
in machine learning, bioinformatics, genomics, and neural computation.  He lives in Irvine, California. 
